{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/new-my-lifestyle-with-headphones/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"945c5ce2-9bf4-5d6a-b6f1-ae4c7c984c9d","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/1f853/headphones.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.59375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/01472/headphones.webp 240w,\n/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/222bd/headphones.webp 480w,\n/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/620b9/headphones.webp 960w,\n/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/86447/headphones.webp 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/3bc27/headphones.jpg 240w,\n/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/98431/headphones.jpg 480w,\n/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/b3ee8/headphones.jpg 960w,\n/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/1f853/headphones.jpg 1024w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/f9a41f4ab07266112f6bd1e7ee40386d/b3ee8/headphones.jpg\"\n          alt=\"About me\"\n          title=\"About me\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>My family presented new headphones to me.  </p>\n<p>WH-CH700N | SONY\n<a href=\"https://www.sony.jp/headphone/products/WH-CH700N/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sony.jp/headphone/products/WH-CH700N/</a>  </p>\n<p>I’m sensitive to sounds from childhood.\nIt’s difficult for me to distinguish human’s voice at a busy place.\nOn the other hand, sometimes I’m get distracted by the slightest sound in a quiet room.</p>\n<p>My friend gave me advice to get a tool for protecting my ears.\nThat’s why I got headphones. It’s so nice.\nI’d like to write about this again on a different day.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/new-my-lifestyle-with-headphones/","tagSlugs":["/tag/headphones/","/tag/hyperacusis/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-30T06:40:32.169Z","description":"I'm sensitive to sounds from childhood. It's difficult for me to distinguish human's voice at a busy place. On the other hand, sometimes I'm get distracted by the slightest sound in a quiet room.","tags":["Headphones","Hyperacusis"],"title":"New My Lifestyle with Headphones","socialImage":"/media/headphones.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/new-my-lifestyle-with-headphones/"}}}